'''巴美列·捷福獎'''（Baillie Gifford Prize）原名'''塞繆爾·約翰遜獎'''（Samuel Johnson Prize，座右銘：“All the Best Stories are True”）是最負盛名的<ref>[http://www.guardian.co.uk/books/2009/may/14/samuel-johnson-prize-shortlist "Science dominates Samuel Johnson prize longlist"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/books/2009/may/14/samuel-johnson-prize-shortlist |date=20090723081100 }}, ''[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]'', 14 May 2009. "..the UK's most prestigious non-fiction award.."</ref><ref name=home>[http://www.thesamueljohnsonprize.co.uk/about-the-prize.htm About the prize] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080704132033/http://www.thesamueljohnsonprize.co.uk/about-the-prize.htm |date=2008-07-04 }}, Samuel Johnson Prize official website. "The UK’s most Prestigious non-fiction award".</ref>非小說類寫作獎之一。塞繆爾·約翰遜獎以作家[[塞繆爾·約翰遜|塞繆爾·約翰遜]]的名字命名，成立於1999年取代了NCR圖書獎（NCR Book Award），資金由一位匿名人士捐贈。獎項評選範圍涵蓋了時政歷史、政治、科學、體育、旅遊、傳記、自傳和藝術<ref name=home/>。2016年由[[巴美列捷福|巴美列捷福]]公司贊助冠軍可獲獎金30,000英鎊而改为现名。

